Package com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.document

Class Document

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.document.Document
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Order
    public abstract class Document
extends java.lang.Object
    The Document class is an abstract class that defines instance variables and methods for a document maintained by a company.
    Author:
    Arthur Vargas
